==Interactions==
While "Strike" cards are generally character specific, cards of different colors can be added by means of the {{R|Prismatic Gem||2}}, {{R|Sea Glass||2}}, or the {{E|Colorful Philosophers|2}}
* {{C|Perfected Strike||2}}: Deals 2 additional damage for ALL your cards containing “Strike”.
* {{C|Hellraiser||2}}: Whenever you draw a card containing “Strike”, it is played against a random enemy.
* {{R|Strike Dummy||2}}: Cards containing “Strike” deal 3 additional damage.
* {{R|Strike Dummy???||2}}: Cards containing “Strike” deal 1 additional damage.
* {{P|Soldier's Stew||2}}: All cards containing "Strike" gain 1 {{KW|Replay||2}} this combat.

===Starter Strike===
* {{R|Large Capsule||2}}: Upon pickup, add an additional Strike and Defend to your Deck.
* {{R|Leafy Poultice||2}}: Upon pickup, Transform 1 of your Strikes.
* {{R|Nutritious Soup||2}}: Upon pickup, {{KW|Enchant||2}} all Strikes in your Deck with {{KW|Tezcatara's Ember||2}}.
* {{R|Pandora's Box||2}}: Transform ALL Strikes.
* {{R|Ghost Seed||2}}: Strikes gain {{KW|Ethereal||2}}.
* {{E|Spirlaing Whirlpool|2}}: {{Frame|Observe}} {{KW|Enchant||2}} a [[Strike]] or [[Defend]] with {{KW|Spiral||2}}.

